{"h02bc6990g84bcg4330g80d2g9bd33df1afd6": ["The last time a subordinate questioned my judgement, I ate tongue stew that very night.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "6df563b0-a5a7-8648-4e2b-f1d412b351bd"], "hbac1e908g96adg40c0ga31dgf831718bb3fb": ["_", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "c427a2ea-f4fe-dbb6-9159-aba88ec9ea4d"], "h0466c86cg94c4g4548g9c0cg7028d1a49e1a": ["<i>*Angry chittering.*</i>", "3538dd40-f37a-45ae-8f2f-6f00e7f4b3e0", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "afe68633-d236-6b6f-b22c-a07e0ec31aaf"], "h88fe2fcegcfbag4f33gbc36gb31187e02a68": ["Had I been permitted to continue, we would not be left without a plan.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "78b61723-da90-14ac-3dcd-bc194a160ca1"], "ha5422e22gd857g450ag9a17g56b67579e301": ["Now, we scout the roads and scan the skies for children of Gith. Purification cannot wait.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "97939435-90d9-54d4-1311-ee3bfaa8a852"], "h1be82e69g1158g40cagb6c1g4bdb9ea92204": ["Subordinate? No - we're partners. You'll treat me with respect.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "7e74219c-061d-f6c1-96c3-16945c24ab1f"], "hc559fdf6g9cc1g4bbbg8c13g688539995750": ["<i>Kainyank.</i> Your tantrum proves you no wiser than a hatchling.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "61822ab6-c818-448e-1af6-dd3ebf11325b"], "h0dd4d8e8g5ac1g4e8fgaf7ag1d0ec7682350": ["The teeth-ling was clear. If there are githyanki west of here, that must be our objective. Purification cannot wait.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "1a844fd7-e7e4-42ac-31d0-ab1abc85c0d2"], "ha011b894g5881g4476ga95fg05487444f2a8": ["<i>Kainyank.</i> Your tantrum proves you no wiser than a hatchling.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "25b97f1b-0aa0-d088-f016-e409fdbfd5cc"], "h8f6ca1c0gf62fg40f0g8d8eg066d71d69efe": ["Had you allowed me to speak, we would not be left without a plan.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "b6a7211a-0166-9ed2-7902-8f92ad6f2357"], "h88e5c379gf31cg4fbfgaa9ag133fd27e8f7d": ["We scout the roads and scan the skies for children of Gith. Purification cannot wait.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "6d7018a9-2dc3-b335-ca33-1faa058cd358"], "h7ba60b0fg4a84g454eg82cbg2203baa7557a": ["You've made your point.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "c169e4fd-c612-a7ad-1c2f-ae69ac08f18b"], "h2ccc989eg7827g47b0gbca7g49a356a370c4": ["Then I needn't make it again.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "d93b1746-e629-0207-0901-2cecc3cf520c"], "h0b734be5gc17eg45ccg9e24g32932b47dc5e": ["<i>Tsk</i>. Had you allowed me to speak, we would not be left without a plan.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "d0dd99ed-e0d4-bc18-1037-ef92461c2f8a"], "hb24c2677g809fg4db5gb15eg9cbe345f8d37": ["If you've finished scowling at me, what comes next?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "cbd49c4f-5328-d953-7dc2-9e349447d43b"], "hb81bc468gcb65g4154g972fg49c5710c8e7f": ["The teeth-ling was clear. If there are githyanki west of here, that must be our objective. Purification cannot wait.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "aca45fb1-3905-640a-4b83-c20e14268824"], "h495c8142ge48eg45dcga8d9g7de4c3581bf2": ["No, no. It's 'Faer\u00fbn'.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "3b3f9196-4152-71dc-d794-d99613c1e9d3"], "hb9cffcc0g3fb9g49c1g82b7g9d8ff8f841d1": ["<i>Tch.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "4017c72a-49cc-8933-d230-2c3170614eb9"], "h5ceaf325g4b89g4942g9550gd6dfb60ef464": ["We are 'tieflings', with an 'f'.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "b274d11c-d496-9b4e-b328-219ad72c4579"], "hbc38f71bgec6cg4cecgb304g34d3bfa2f154": ["I believe it is 'tiefling'.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "b274d11c-d496-9b4e-b328-219ad72c4579"], "h5c301c62g488cg487dga379g86ebc3040e63": ["Heh - did you say 'teeth-ling'?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "b274d11c-d496-9b4e-b328-219ad72c4579"], "hb0d74fb2gd62dg4fdagbbfbg7ec9f7d85d77": ["I stand <i>corrected.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "ec199c6b-e742-0cd3-69d5-e797b5b46b00"], "hf583b466g6e06g4c60gaeb3gfe8307bcf212": ["I am unfamiliar with the - well, I shall not say 'culture'. 'Custom', perhaps.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "e92283f5-67ab-62e5-7060-f3863cc66120"], "h10ac775cg9d4bg444ag8bdbgf972ff0179be": ["You will educate me on matters of this Fay-run.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "3391af02-5f73-5803-bb69-9b319834b3ab"], "h0931226fg717fg49fegb313gd7310d24497b": ["I don't know this protocol. What does purification entail?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "dec9b4ea-bacb-b71f-e61e-9c731af2caf6"], "hb61ffda4g83c5g4142g91eeg2fa231ef52f2": ["What do you mean, 'purification'?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "dec9b4ea-bacb-b71f-e61e-9c731af2caf6"], "h2b123001g5c9ag46fagab9bg6fe291ed2cbd": ["The cr\u00e8che holds the <i>Zaith'isk. </i>It will cleanse us of the parasite.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "99e7e555-0eb0-0355-2cfc-55be27058e09"], "hc1837163ge611g4f11g9f34gdeb74ca0fac5": ["By Vlaakith's covenant, I know little more.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "cf0ff0a8-498c-5135-679c-622507ca147a"], "he63c4a79gff6eg45b6ga9fbg6aea1d034b37": ["By covenant, I can say no more.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "cf0ff0a8-498c-5135-679c-622507ca147a"], "h9f09a679gfca9g4944gbd36g92e0081e9f61": ["<i>Are her intentions sincere? Watch closely for signs of deceit.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "517432af-2100-d7cb-6d09-67e2ad1f726a"], "h1678fc74g8f71g42dag8b1cg4d332796e872": ["*Lae'zel's eyes drift downward. Something is off.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "39a746bd-7c2b-6ce1-9ab4-1ec3a8791109"], "h6d866481g3925g4a60gb6a6g38ab188d5388": ["*A strange sensation courses through you, and your companion's mind unfolds, secrets half-revealed.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "e6e7ed5b-0331-3a38-450c-faaeb2707b9b"], "he462b6d1g1a68g4357ga03dg7fa5f584b349": ["There's something else you want to say. Spit it out.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "455958cf-7206-dce6-b576-31d7d690e9aa"], "h58ef3c11g88b4g440dg8c29gc989d290f6a6": ["An infinitude. ", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "933d3fba-f4fc-ab17-6d13-ee7cd346003b"], "he09975ddg1ca2g440fg9a8dgbb0de35e2ed7": ["We are not friends. I will speak when it suits me, and not before.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "4322839f-00ab-abf0-cb13-c24100374bba"], "h2dff79ccg7a4fg4209g9189g61a2c4d88db3": ["<i>Enter Lae'zel's mind.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "1626a0ec-08db-9d0f-29ca-5543cd440804"], "h782bb8bagc2ceg4939g8efbgb42eeead6955": ["*You see yourself through Lae'zel's eyes. To her, you are already a mind flayer - a monster in all but appearance.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "061b296a-5525-5c37-5a06-cc1ac6d2cc94"], "hdb4a21f0g9929g4b52gab16g6c1930e2969b": ["*A shiver runs across your mind... you feel sated.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "ba32c642-6133-6c90-3516-8a823e457567"], "h9786bb41gbb84g44f3g85d3g04e2b8094958": ["Are we finished?", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "6d978384-034d-8cfc-ca93-aeef782f551a"], "hf3de010fg6a7fg412dgb671g6e657fb55aac": ["We shall find this cr\u00e8che. I know we shall not fail.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "f27bab25-c26e-8b38-7d8d-e25a8a1e1e48"], "h166a385bg83c4g4a96g80fag3e014b5489d7": ["We'll be finished once we find this cr\u00e8che. I think we'll make it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "f27bab25-c26e-8b38-7d8d-e25a8a1e1e48"], "h8d93b11ag2f75g4932g88e9g698a194e8bb3": ["You've done well to place your trust in me, kin.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "c9215057-d6f6-a4ff-9df9-cead4834c1da"], "h06289396g5cefg4af7g8ac3g669884114324": ["Well done. You have learned to place your faith in Githyanki.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "c9215057-d6f6-a4ff-9df9-cead4834c1da"], "h174d08e6g8127g494cg86bage3575d19ae40": ["I fear time is too short to reach this cr\u00e8che in time.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "2743e7a6-a269-2534-102a-f8a92abf87a3"], "hedee78a1g0529g418bg8958g069c481bd22b": ["We may not manage to find this cr\u00e8che in time, you know.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "2743e7a6-a269-2534-102a-f8a92abf87a3"], "h1cac2e3fg19bbg4efdg862cga2cabb7ec285": ["Fear not. Should you turn, I will simply cut you down.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "c0242790-567c-9662-e3b2-261a496d35d3"], "haaa774ffg9235g4d77g875bge169cceef339": ["I don't like how you look at me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "dbba1e77-b8f0-aacb-0e3f-896b040a42e0"], "h0909781dg01efg4bc6g9420g317b1487a3ac": ["I see you as you are. What you think is of no concern to me.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "595501cc-8afc-4656-c954-2191c0f9b930"], "h8417e0aag6e7ag48acg902dg14b08373a7dc": ["I am accustomed to disdain. But you see me as an abomination.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "41a84b4b-8dcc-5cda-3461-a1bfc666e936"], "hdf58ca4fg124eg41b7g8724gdf560f69eccb": ["And so you are, for as long as the tadpole infects you.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "e2a03153-10a5-8add-a5ce-464232573d3c"], "ha5bedf53g3085g45a7g8b0dgfe6c0431e31c": ["But fear not. Should you turn, I will simply cut you down.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "a26551c7-747d-ab91-f3a4-fdef7641ecdb"], "hb7757482gb7f5g4196g91d1g2d708e5f81ca": ["*Something stirs deep within you, hungry and alert... it's taking something you'll never get back.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "a6e12c12-17a1-0d91-5c6a-27978de93bce"], "hb2252511g2390g4ab1g86fagec0cf3a3f12f": ["*Your mind lurches, reeling suddenly as if... bitten.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "bf9ad7a5-e839-11f1-cf5d-b4cf662da0ba"], "hd3d1235fg0320g46cagabf0gea9dc7daea38": ["*A shadow swims across your vision, and a familiar voice tells you to be calm. You are loved.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "be28adca-3b4c-36c1-ee9b-012e361b8af0"], "h1a8a2590g2670g48c3g80c0g20e06f9bc97e": ["*Your blood runs quicker, feeding the gnawing absence at the centre of your mind.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "3e7e2f35-ab32-3a49-564b-6dca6bdc976d"], "h2ca2ad19g36feg4265g8eaeg59cd10b87ed4": ["*The presence deep in your mind is awake, unblinking. This is it. A single word pervades your consciousness: 'Soon'.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "efa2316b-abce-5861-b705-a40747cb936f"], "hb6134a48g2b79g421ag8ce0g7ee87a687ffe": ["*Your mind is full, bursting with ecstasy and terror. Finally, it is coming. You are becoming.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "6ab655ba-cc6d-2f6d-4dfa-35295f675aa8"], "h60157157gf577g43ddg8cadg7372bc3f8fac": ["<i>Enter Lae'zel's mind.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "454b330b-b817-52e3-3d64-30ca737ff201"], "h512ae730g16c1g4bd7g9f61ga3e2f26d4785": ["Out. And do not try it again, <i>kainyank.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "8d41f941-623c-7e8e-0059-46726c0ae735"], "h290d9eb2g622cg4bb7gb2ffg8a78da281e03": ["<i>Draw on the power within to enforce your will.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "b3bfc2ef-0d73-8646-3524-544a3d885e27"], "h95177e98g97a2g4cc0gad1bg2e083cb80377": ["*You focus on the source of the power, but it is quiet and still. It needs to rest.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "d3faef90-3798-4a94-3afa-1c5f2ce73e8c"], "hb928cbb5gf5f7g4016gbcddg3065c58af90e": ["<i>Draw on the power within to enforce your will.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "4726c283-6ebe-0fcc-4a10-d25d65f96656"], "hc24ddf6egfd60g49d9ga857g0ab672a2a3f3": ["*You see nothing unusual in Lae'zel's demeanour.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "2110cb4c-3950-6417-7139-1ea96b220bf3"], "h45ab0670gbae1g4a78g99e8g7722aa930977": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "ee74636e-1df9-4f92-428f-db37b4d44c13"], "h47c8734cg8df6g4635gbc9eg0b44c8ab5970": ["<i>Tsk</i>. I might have a plan had you allowed me to speak.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "6f520971-1751-3989-6568-a46af968bc5b"], "h1143bc0bg3d00g4711ga3f4gcc6eefc53fca": ["We scout the roads and scan the skies for children of Gith. Purification cannot wait.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "87afeb58-767c-e3fb-4e46-89d7ece24a66"], "hc7e7623cgbe95g4447gbff9g4cef086c38b4": ["You might dine on my fist next - I do not hold with torture.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "58e01021-b080-4791-251f-1f1f3008ff10"], "h79cf6613gff64g4c7egb7b4ga0d1d30d9e76": ["_", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "fc799822-d574-b558-5cc5-f962a4f0ffc8"], "h783ae4c1g0a7bg4be1gb784gbd6f1fbbe622": ["_", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "f4bd47d3-cfb0-2ba6-50d2-bad16f684015"], "h7731949dg72eeg4062ga0d6g5056537d63c1": ["You will speak to drow with <i>respect.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "a34085ca-9aae-55cf-252b-c5ab158045d2"], "h9fb1c8d0gb689g4596g860cg394b8e6ef0fd": ["We are githyanki. You will approach with <i>respect.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "c3cd77a3-1bb7-98f2-defa-aac9b19502af"], "h7d60c1aag3893g4546g9101geb359ff1a601": ["You shouldn't have to be so rough with him.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "8484ce24-4c76-9d43-c8cc-0731726fddfd"], "h39b75adfgef97g4560gad77gd5ddb9be790d": ["Goodness me - that's a terrible way to make friends. Must you be so rough?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "4f6374f4-f65e-e81c-1bcd-313a8c2359ca"], "ha1de836aga65fg4b0fgaea4g38ca19ae3805": ["Such cruelty. Is your heart really so cold?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "4dc99d90-0b86-d8de-ae22-df75a0264f60"], "h9d7bece5gc850g4366ga26bgfef5eea9eedd": ["I warned you, didn't I? You ought to reconsider keeping her around, before she causes <i>real</i> trouble.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "508773b7-478d-80f3-501a-d3b3e2b69a9b"], "h0176bdc5gee91g4507g8759g7435037bdeaf": ["Your kind proves compliant. A useful trait.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "d3e4f3cd-f593-73af-8650-f0dad63b60ad"], "h5f3dadc2g6b5fg425agb6ebg1176b11b272b": ["The locals prove compliant. A useful trait.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "d3e4f3cd-f593-73af-8650-f0dad63b60ad"], "h75291069ga0d7g4101g9b77g269b6a0bbaa6": ["_", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "eda64cb4-fa47-2cd5-268d-01e524fe56c2"], "h763a739dgb878g4f53g959dg2f076d7542df": ["Do you plan to be that rough with everyone we meet?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "604aca2e-a5a6-3cbb-5fb4-9b997709d959"], "hf2572a51gfd72g46eegbd95g1e7890af608d": ["<i>Rough?</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "6963badd-7c08-cc95-2fe2-da2f42b9a2d0"], "h4b153ab9gb765g49e8gbe42g628f4a54f721": ["Soon, you will be vomiting blood and tearing apart your own flesh.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "62d898ed-9482-58e3-0f1d-738b87b0923d"], "h79f9943ag1831g4f40ga754g8b4838619f7e": ["When the tentacles sprout from your lips, will you still cry that I was <i>rough?</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "e5a85641-c1c7-a7c8-eac0-a4d55101c8ff"], "h68d17af2g070bg4ab7gb8ccg2164b5e971f3": ["<i>Enough. </i>Just tell me what's our next move.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "37488ac7-2930-745f-2493-245463ce61b9"], "hed59ae0cgab68g4658g9c62g4109cc11a6a9": ["All right. You made your point.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "8c2357c5-009e-66b8-52ba-558716e23cec"], "h03139270gee55g4b59gb48agc8683d94237d": ["Then I needn't make it again.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "42358785-5a48-cd0e-a414-b50e433f33e9"], "hcc9c0a91g460dg4274g8f47g9481dbca7a25": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "c3f6bc00-1a48-ef72-37d6-4640bbdc4240"], "hdf16e41eg18ebg4811g8651g046f544e244e": ["I'll grant you this much, Lae'zel - you're not the worst interrogator I've ever seen.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "184e821c-4df4-b278-fda7-4e6a33e8cc71"], "h80eaa641g4490g4559g9e9cg9122e975925a": ["An admirable interrogation technique. Very efficient.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "184e821c-4df4-b278-fda7-4e6a33e8cc71"], "h0aed86b7g39feg40dbg86b2gfa89aeda54e2": ["You're a dab hand at interrogations - we might need that skill again.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "184e821c-4df4-b278-fda7-4e6a33e8cc71"], "hb9d3ad87gc3feg4f5eg85a7g0bc055786f60": ["<i>Chk. </i>A shell so thin requires little to crack it.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "4f5d39b3-41fa-1710-83f0-58c993c5720b"], "hc17b6592g8dfcg4ef7g81dag687d4aea3537": ["What comes next?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "bba66cb6-7cba-3390-15e0-cc25fec393f1"], "hef80cf33g1129g4602g8d03g0639634df5a7": ["Zorru was an easy mark. Don't get complacent.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "9a56a71b-8f49-e800-d869-7a833551072b"], "h7870b3cfg0536g4f9dg8c63g38318d3075ad": ["<i>Chk. </i>A thin shell requires little to crack it. I will apply more pressure should the situation demand.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "853c5688-d1be-2085-e6ae-e7b009c2a081"], "h8e9dd40agacb7g4a06gbb3fg56f9215e3357": ["Goodness me - we'll make no friends that way. Must you be so rough?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "4ac29430-239d-13f2-f8a8-6ac39919d61f"], "ha2da1dfeg7a89g489eg8afegda6eb18cb880": ["I beg your pardon. Was I too <i>rough?</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "d975e956-6800-0976-d689-84ff627f6479"], "h99b9a47cgc669g4c3fgb241g2e125664f75d": ["You shouldn't have to be so rough with him.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "7b65daf9-9482-1484-2796-b1ee523f0fa8"], "hd1ee4ad6g2c01g4eb2g8cb9g6916343c2366": ["Tieflings aren't compliant - we're survivors.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "62961707-de9e-f32d-8228-f63e910b9dd7"], "ha90e23d3gc2e6g4f1ag9cf6ge20e4b10450c": ["<i>Cockroaches </i>are survivors. Yet I do not congratulate them.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "2747abb4-0de1-35c1-c524-15c20c0bbc28"], "hf145c170g8495g4ecega9b9g2cc1af467caa": ["Such cruelty. Is your heart really so cold?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "e9a8a96b-fc8d-d6dd-3ee9-400a63f4e4c6"], "h94fcc701gf6dbg415eg8cf1gbf9b312cb75e": ["<i>Cold?</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "6f0f4cae-0b04-0c3d-f95f-f7c1c0b3d9c9"], "h154a5b37g1782g4f9bg91ddg7e3b7e0e75a0": ["Soon, you will be vomiting blood and tearing apart your own flesh.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "42b2bd0f-a26c-8496-6ce5-2fd07fe880de"], "h49358007ga406g4bebg91a1g9974b5f9828d": ["When the tentacles sprout from your lips, will you still cry that I was <i>cold?</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\World_Relationship_Dialogs\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_WRD_LaezelCreche.html", "3a0c2552-cdb5-4231-8218-99c8554332e7"]}